{
  "stem": "1183.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that was the third time, and the last time my father saved my life, because at the time I was 15 years old.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I had to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My father took me outside of the camp at that time that that day was on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He talked with one of the officers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I didn't see him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I had to wait outside while I was witness to lots of women and women on stretchers who had just given birth.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Baby-- in the little-- premature babies in the little basket were outside to be hauled onto buses.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Before that, I-- just a short while before that happened, I met a relative of mine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And it was an aunt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was a relative of my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She was there with her two children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And by coincidence, I met her because her name was van Bingen, and that was my mother's maiden name.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I was quite happy to have a relative there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "At that time, the coincidence how I met her-- at first-- at that time still for me in the camp, and a little bit embarrassing-- I just caught lice, head lice.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And it was horrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And she just met me when I had one of those things on my head, to, to get rid of the lice.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "That just was an incident, because of the most time that you want to have a relative, I met her.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And it was nice to have her, although for a brief time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And what I remember always-- because I was waiting for the officers of the SS [GERMAN] outside the camp, close.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And she was-- came out with her two children, and she called me to join her in the bus.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I said, no I can't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I have to wait for my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
